As a result I directed the convening of a hearing on 10 November a transcript of which can be found, inter alia, on the Bailii website (
		http://www.bailii.org/
	      ) under the Bailii Citation Number: [2009] EWHC B35 (Admin).  As a result of that hearing further directions were given concerning disclosure of documents and the filing of further evidence and written submissions.  Following a further hearing on 11 December 2009 the timetable envisaged by those directions was varied and indeed the timetable that replaced it was itself modified further to accommodate the parties who needed further time to deal with the issues involved.
